\subtree{
\title{Data Sovereignty}
\p{Iroh enables \strong{true data sovereignty}:}

\ul{
\li{✅ \strong{You own your node} — No registration required}
\li{✅ \strong{Direct connections} — No central server}
\li{✅ \strong{End-to-end encrypted} — Even peers see encrypted data}
\li{✅ \strong{Offline capable} — Local-first with eventual sync}
\li{✅ \strong{Portable} — Move your node anywhere}
}

\p{This is the foundation of nextgen protocols: decentralized, user-controlled infrastructure.}
}

